text: Her swutelad on þisum gewrite hwylce gerihta langon into Tantune on þam timan þe Eadwerd cing wes cucu & dead.

Þæt is ærest of þam lande æt Nigonhidon seo mann redden into Tantune cirhsceattas & burhgerihtu, heorðpenegas & hundred penegas & teoþung of ælcere hide eahta penegas, hamsocn & forsteall, griþbrice & handfangenþeof, aþ & ordel, fyrdwite & eall swa oft swa him ma bude to gemote he come ofþe hine man badode.
Dunna wes þæs biscopes mann to þam timan þe Eadward cing wæs cucu & dead of þam lande æt Acon & of Taalande & of twam Cedenon.
& he geaf to gerihton V circsceattas & heorðpenegas & hundredpenegas, hamsocne & forsteall, griðbrice & handfangenne þeof, aþ & ordel & þriwa secan gemot onXIImonþum.
And Ealdreð wæs þæs biscopes mann of þam lande æt Hele & dyde þe ilcan gerihta þæ ma dyde of Nigonhidon.
And of þam fif hidon æt Baggabeorgan,IIIcircsceattas & burgerihta, heorðpenegas & hundredpenegas & handfangene þeof, aþ & ordel, hamsocn & forsteall, griðbrice & þreo motlæþu ungeboden onXIImonþum.
Of Lidigerde,Icircsceatt & eall þe geilcan gerihta þe ma dyde of Baggabeorge.
Of Hylle,Icircsceatt & burhgerihtu, heorðpenegas & hundreðpenegas, hamsocne & forsteall, griðbrice & handfangene þeof, aþ & ordel &IIIgemot on geare buton he hit gebicge oþþe gebidde.
Of þære oþre healfre hide æt twam Holaforda,IIcircsceattas & eall þæ geylcan gerihta þe ma deð of Cedon.

Ðises ys gewitnes, Gisa bisceop & ælfsie abbod & Wulgeat abbod & ælfnod mynsterprauost & Wulfwerd wita & Godwine Eadwies sunu & ælmer þæs abbodes broþor & ælgelric æt Healswege & Heardinc Eadnoðes sunu & Garmund & ælfric tigel & Ordgar se wite & ælfwerd Leofsunes sunu & Brichtric se calewa & Dodda æt Curi & ælmer werl & Sæwold æt Iliacum & Wulfric æt Pauleshele & Ealdred æt Sulfhere & Wulger æt Hiwerc & æilwine wunge.
